---
description: Strict allowlist of permitted packages
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

Do NOT install packages not on this list without explicit approval.

Frontend (allowed):
- react, react-dom
- vite, @vitejs/plugin-react
- typescript
- tailwindcss, postcss, autoprefixer
- @radix-ui/* (any Radix primitive)
- class-variance-authority, clsx, tailwind-merge
- lucide-react

Backend (allowed):
- fastapi, uvicorn
- pydantic, pydantic-settings
- PyMuPDF (fitz)
- httpx
- pytest, pytest-asyncio

Do NOT add:
- State management (Redux, Zustand, Jotai)
- Routing (React Router)
- CSS-in-JS libraries
- WebSocket libraries (socket.io, ws)
- Gemini SDK on backend
- Database ORMs (SQLAlchemy)
- Authentication libraries
